# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo

# AI governance generated by `sdg-agents init`
# This repo is the generator: the .ai/ tree is a mirror of src/assets/, whose
# source of truth is already versioned. Only the backlog is exempt, because it
# holds knowledge no other file carries. Git will not descend into an excluded
# directory, so re-including it takes one negation per level.
.ai/*
!.ai/backlog/
.ai/backlog/*
!.ai/backlog/context.md
!.ai/backlog/stack.md
!.ai/backlog/learned.md
!.ai/backlog/troubleshoot.md
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md

# Volatile session state. Already covered by `.ai/backlog/*` above, but
# writeGitignore() matches literal lines: drop these and every dogfood run
# appends them back.
.ai/backlog/tasks.md
.ai/backlog/impact-map.md
.ai/last-prompt.md

# Scratch
tmp/
temp/
